These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: iced-tea, tea, soy-milk
1. Beverage:tea is on the right of Beverage:soy-milk##1
2. Beverage:iced-tea is on the far right##1
3. Beverage:iced-tea is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | tea | iced-tea |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: martial-arts, animation, western
1. Movie-Genre:animation is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:martial-arts is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | western | animation |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Sport: skateboarding, water-polo, cycling
1. Sport:water-polo is in an even position##4
2. Sport:water-polo is on the left or right of Sport:cycling##3
3. Sport:cycling is on the right of Sport:water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Sport   | skateboarding | water-polo | cycling |

 #################################
 
